data.description: Newly built home. Welcome to this charming 4/2/3 home that effortlessly combines modern comfort with classic design. As you step through the front door, you are greeted by a spacious and inviting living area, perfect for both entertaining guests and relaxing with your family. The kitchen is great for entertaining with a huge island and features stainless steel appliances, & stylish cabinetry. This home has large bedrooms offering plenty of space for everyone. The home boasts thoughtful details throughout with modern fixtures, tile floors, carpet in bedrooms, granite countertops, and a 3-car garage great for storage. This home has a fenced oversized yard sized at .31 acres. Plenty of room for a pool, guest house, fire pit, playground, space to park your boat and much more!
